overview.zh: 我们正在完善 Element在 imToken 中的代币相关资料。完成后，大家可以在 imToken 里看到 logo，更方便地管理 Element，同时能看到更多代币信息。
overview.en: Element.Black (ELT) is a web 3.0 blockchain infrastructure that strives to innovate the entertainment industry.ELT creates an interactive and immersive cyber community that revolutionize entertainment financing and monetization.Applications of ELT is based on the Element Token (symbol: ELT), with a total token number of 2 billion, which will be listed on decentralized exchanges for the community to trade
